display_long_description:
**Climb, Ascend, Together!**

Welcome to **Free** Only Up VR Multiplayer – a physics-based virtual reality adventure that challenges you to reach new heights—literally. Inspired by the chaotic realism of Boneworks movement and the addictive verticality of Only Up, this game throws you and your friends into a towering world full of floating platforms, intense parkour, and unpredictable physics. So—do you have what it takes to go Up?

# New Update: Goodbye Legs, Hello Chaos!
Yep, they’re gone. Legs? Deleted. In this update, it’s all arms, all skill, and all-out madness. Use pure upper body strength and physics-driven VR movement to climb your way through a brutal vertical world.
[media]


# Wait—don’t forget! It’s multiplayer.
Climb with friends, race to the top, or just laugh as you all fall together. Whether you're helping or trolling each other, it’s always better **(and funnier)** with people. [media]

# No legs. No mercy. Just you and friends, your hands, and the climb.
[media]
